    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/0e3cd7d3d8f638b59e1df5dca0fce663.avif?t=1758326429\" width=616 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>小森林面包师</strong>》是一款充满悠闲疗愈氛围的2D像素游戏，你将扮演莉莉亚，一位初来乍到白林镇的新手面包师。你将接管一家曾经由面包大师经营的面包店，踏上成为面包大师的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/892566705f2c3ec3e389e76b0a0aba5b.avif?t=1758326429\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/69cc5c3163a657314b11abe6f6ef108b.webp?t=1758326429\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/69cc5c3163a657314b11abe6f6ef108b.poster.avif?t=1758326429\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=100 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在森林迷宫中收集各式各样、用来制作烘焙食品的食材。有时新食材还会激发新食谱的灵感！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索神秘的荒野和森林，你会在那里遇到可爱的小精灵，与他们互动以收集特殊食材。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁更多探索地区并发现不同的景观。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索时，可以装备各种护符以获得不同的收集加成。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/1733a516c0608927c8bcdd317a67457d.poster.avif?t=1758326429\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/1733a516c0608927c8bcdd317a67457d.webm?t=1758326429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/1733a516c0608927c8bcdd317a67457d.mp4?t=1758326429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的小动物总是惹人喜爱。森林或荒野中会出现小精灵，你可以与动物和精灵互动。有些动物可能想跟你一起回家！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/62719f937cd82371139a7bd55cdcc1a8.poster.avif?t=1758326429\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/62719f937cd82371139a7bd55cdcc1a8.webm?t=1758326429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/62719f937cd82371139a7bd55cdcc1a8.mp4?t=1758326429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作美味且温暖人心的面包和蛋糕，同时也提高你的声誉。当然，别忘了付房租。请注意，您的名气越大，你就越有可能吸引臭名昭著的王国面包师行会的注意。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你的名气越来越大，解锁更多的房间和设备来满足客户日益增长的需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现各种食谱以满足客户的期望。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/1c1933d60c2635098691b379a697337e.webp?t=1758326429\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/1c1933d60c2635098691b379a697337e.poster.avif?t=1758326429\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019200/extras/b713db9ee86657cc47965a0d0bd1da19.avif?t=1758326429\" width=616 height=1041 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与迷人的镇民成为朋友，深入了解他们的故事。成为白林镇的一员！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和恋爱候选人谈恋爱，他们可能是吸血鬼、矮人或德鲁伊。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解更多白林镇的故事。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于开发者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>小森林面包师</strong>》目前由一人开发。在此世界里，你可以用自己的步调轻松探索，了解关于小镇和居民的小故事。愿这个游戏在忙碌的生活之外能为你带来一些治愈感，这是我制作这个游戏的初衷，希望你喜欢这个我用爱制作的游戏。💛</p>",
